OL,3,CFormer NI secretary tells Covid-19
OL,4,CInquiry of Stormont collapse 'concerns'
OL,6,FFormer Northern Ireland secretary Sir
OL,7,FBrandon Lewis said he feared the
OL,8,FStormont Executive could collapse in
OL,9,Fautumn 2020, as tensions rose between
OL,10,Fministers about whether to extend
OL,11,FCovid restrictions.
OL,13,FGiving evidence to the UK Covid-19
OL,14,FInquiry, Sir Brandon also said he had
OL,15,Fbeen surprised when the Irish
OL,16,FGovernment shut schools in the early
OL,17,Fmonths of the pandemic, just a day
OL,18,Fafter he had had a conversation with
OL,19,Fthe country's deputy premier about the
OL,20,Fneed for consistent messaging across
OL,21,Fthe island.
