OL,6,FThe Stormont powersharing institutions
OL,7,Fwere restored in January 2020
OL,8,Ffollowing a three-year collapse.
OL,10,FBut the new Executive found itself
OL,11,Fimmediately faced with the challenge
OL,12,Fof coping with the Covid pandemic,
OL,13,Fintroducing a series of restrictions
OL,14,Fto attempt to limit the virus spread.
OL,16,FIn November, during a series of
OL,17,FExecutive meetings, Stormont ministers
OL,18,Fstruggled to agree on extensions to
OL,19,Flockdown measures as the second wave
OL,20,Fof the virus spread.
