OL,6,F"It wasn't about so much the decisions
OL,7,Fper se, it was about the process,
OL,8,Fpapers coming late or inappropriate,
OL,9,Fpeople leaking things during the
OL,10,Fmeeting.
OL,12,F"There was a real frustration with
OL,13,Feach other. It was a very, very
OL,14,Fdifficult period."
OL,16,FSir Brandon said tensions in the
OL,17,FExecutive had spilled over into the
OL,18,Fpublic following the attendance of
OL,19,FSinn Fein members at the funeral of
OL,20,Frepublican Bobby Storey in June 2020.
