OL,6,FHe also pointed out that Sir David
OL,7,FSterling had retired as head of the
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland Civil Service in
OL,9,FAugust 2020 but then-first minister
OL,10,FArlene Foster and then-deputy first
OL,11,Fminister Michelle O'Neill had been
OL,12,Funable to agree on a replacement.
OL,14,FThe inquiry was also shown a readout
OL,15,Ffrom a telephone conversation between
OL,16,FSir Brandon and then-tanaiste Simon
OL,17,FCoveney on March 11 2020.
