OL,6,FSir Brandon said: "Absolutely right,
OL,7,Fyes.
OL,9,F"It certainly did cause an issue. Only
OL,10,Fdays before, myself and Simon Coveney
OL,11,Fwere discussing how we work together,
OL,12,Fkeep each other informed, if there are
OL,13,Fgoing to be differences, which there
OL,14,Fare likely to be with two sovereign
OL,15,Fgovernments making decisions and the
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland Executive with their
OL,17,Fpowers, so that we at least understand
OL,18,Fwhat they are so we can manage them.
