OL,6,F"And then we were all taken by
OL,7,Fsurprise. I was actually in Washington
OL,8,FDC when the taoiseach (Irish premier)
OL,9,Fwent out in Washington and made that
OL,10,Fannouncement.
OL,12,F"It was a complete surprise to
OL,13,Feverybody and that was surprising,
OL,14,Fbearing in mind we had all just been
OL,15,Ftalking about working together."
OL,17,FHe added: "It immediately put a
OL,18,Fquestion mark, if the Irish Government
OL,19,Fhave got a reason to do this, why is
OL,20,Fnot everybody else doing this?
